Description: Binding to the GTK+ OpenGL Extension${haskell:ShortBlurb}
 GtkGLExt provides the GDK objects to support OpenGL rendering in GTK+, and
 GtkWidget API add-ons to make GTK+ widgets OpenGL-capable.
 .
